===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

# A [[craft]] used for [[transportation]] of goods, fishing, racing, recreational cruising, or military use on or in the [[water]], [[propelled]] by [[oar]]s or [[outboard motor]] or inboard [[motor]] or by [[wind]].
# {{context|poker slang}} A [[full house]].
# {{chemistry}} One of two possible [[conformation]]s of [[cyclohexane]] rings (the other being [[chair]]), shaped roughly like a boat.

====Usage notes====
There's no explicit limit, but the word '''''boat''''' usually refers to a relatively small watercraft that is generally smaller than a "[[ship]]" and larger than a "[[dinghy]]".

